data.name: lblPageNumbersHelp.ToolTip
data.value: You can delimit the page numbers using any combination of commas, semi-colons, or spaces. You can also intermix page number ranges such as 3-7, 12-14, etc. Note: page numbers which are not in the original document will be ignored.

data.name: lblCaption.Text
data.value: This mini-application is used for extracting the specified pages from each pdf file and overwriting the original pdf with the changes or optionally saving the extracted pages of the original pdf to a new file of the same name and path but with the specified suffix appended to the end of the file name.
